import React from 'react'; import './Process.css'; const Process = () => { return (
{/* Desktop */}

Process

Our team proposed a redesign of the personal account into a user-friendly dashboard for intuitive navigation and quick access to essential information, addressing research-identified pain points.

Key updates:

  • Notifications: Real-time order and special offer updates.
  • Payment Methods: Added management for saved payment options.
  • Active Orders: Dedicated section for current order details.
  • Exclusive Deals: Highlighted special offers from the company and partners.
  • Redesigned Order Page: Enhanced for a more intuitive experience.
  • Onboarding Flow: Guided users through the new interface and features.
{/* Tablet */}

  • Redesigned Order Page: Enhanced for a more intuitive experience.
  • Onboarding Flow: Guided users through the new interface and features.
